const bodyParser = require("body-parser")

How to setup Node And Express

cmd:

Step 1: Create Folder
mkdir express-server

Step 2: Create Server File
touch server.js

Step 3: Initialize npm
npm init

Step 4: How to Install Express
npm install express

Step 5: Run File Using cmd
node server.js

Step 6: How to install Nodemon
npm install -g nodemon

Step 7:bodyParser for post request
npm install body-parser
it is used to take input from user
